	(text_box "Display (DISP1 - HS20H5072RX) - the primary user interface for displaying menus, status and phone information. The MCU communicates with the display over an SPI interface (CS, DC, SCL and SDA), while RESET allows the MCU to hardware reset the display controller if required. The display logic and LCD power are supplied from +3.3V_SW, allowing James' load switch to completely disconnect the display when not in use. LEDA/LEDK connect to the separate backlight driver circuit, enabling independent brightness control."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 383.54 200.66 0)
		(size 68.58 17.78)
		(margins 0.9525 0.9525 0.9525 0.9525)
		(stroke
